@startuml Request Lifecycle Pipeline
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam activityArrowThickness 2

|#LightCyan|Middleware|
start
:1. **cookie-parser**
Parse cookies from request headers;

:2. **CORS**
Validate origin, set credentials headers;

:3. **RequestContextMiddleware**
Extract IP, user-agent, set request ID;

|#LightGreen|Pipe|
:4. **ValidationPipe** (global)
class-validator + class-transformer;

note right
  Returns structured error
  with errorCode on
  validation failure
end note

|#LightYellow|Guard|
:5. **Guard**
(AuthGuard / MicroserviceGuard / ApiKeyGuard);
split
  :Token/key extraction;
split again
  :JWT validation +
  Redis session check;
split again
  :@EndpointKey →
  dynamic permission check
  (Redis → DB fallback);
end split

:Sets request.user (AuthUser);

|#LightPink|Interceptor|
:6. **HttpMetricsInterceptor**
Start timing;

|#LightBlue|Handler|
:7. **Controller method execution**
Service → Repository → DB;

|#LightPink|Interceptor|
:8. **ClassSerializerInterceptor**
Entity serialization (where applied);

:HttpMetricsInterceptor
Record duration + status code;

|#Salmon|Filter|
if (Unhandled exception?) then (yes)
  :9. **AllExceptionsFilter**
  - Cause chain traversal
  - Winston structured logging
  - JSON error response;
else (no)
  :Return response;
endif

stop
@enduml
